name: Pset_ElectricFlowStorageDeviceTypeCommon
definition: The characteristics of the supply associated with an electrical device occurrence acting as a source of supply to an electrical distribution system NOTE: Properties within this property set should ONLY be used in circumstances when an electrical supply is applied. The property set, the properties contained and their values are not applicable to a circumstance where the sypply  is not being applied to the eletrical system or is temporarily disconnected. All properties within this property set are considered to represent a steady state situation.

localizations.name: elektrisches Speichergerät - allgemeiner Eigenschaftssatz
localizations.definition: Die Eigenschaften der Versorgung, die mit einem Auftreten eines elektrischen Geräts verbunden sind, das als Quelle für die Versorgung eines elektrischen Verteilersystems fungiert, HINWEIS: Die Eigenschaften innerhalb dieses Eigenschaftssatzes sollten NUR unter den Umständen verwendet werden, unter denen eine elektrische Versorgung angewendet wird.

properties.name: Reference
properties.definition: Reference ID for this specified type in this project (e.g. type 'A-1'), provided, if there is no classification reference to a recognized classification system used.

localizations.name: 参照
localizations.definition: 当該プロジェクトで定義する形式の参照ID（例：A-1)、承認された分類に存在しないときに使用される。

localizations.name: 참조
localizations.definition: 해당 프로젝트에 정의된 형식의 참조 ID (예 : A-1) 승인된 분류에 존재하지 않을 때 사용된다.

properties.name: Status
properties.definition: Status of the element, predominately used in renovation or retrofitting projects. The status can be assigned to as "New" - element designed as new addition, "Existing" - element exists and remains, "Demolish" - element existed but is to be demolished,  "Temporary" - element will exists only temporary (like a temporary support structure).

localizations.name: 状態
localizations.definition: 要素（主にリノベーションまたは改修プロジェクトにおいて）の状態。 状態は、「新規(New)」－新しく追加される要素。「既存」－要素は存在し、かつ残りもの。「破壊」－要素は存在したが、廃棄されるもの。「一時的」－一時的に存在する要素（一時的にサポートしている構造のようなもの）。

constantValues.name: EXISTING
constantValues.definition: element exists and is to remain

constantValues.name: DEMOLISH
constantValues.definition: element exists but is to be demolished

constantValues.name: TEMPORARY
constantValues.definition: element will exist only temporarily (such as a temporary support structure)
